<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民们都躲到了树桩后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空、悟净和八戒都拿起了兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只巨大的老龟露出了水面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是只巨大的老龟！”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老龟向悟空行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那妖怪占了我的水府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢谢你赶走了他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老龟又看向村民们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不用造船了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会驮着他们过河的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那太好了！”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来自大唐，我......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是谁。”老龟打断了唐僧的话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是去西天取经的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道你们会经过我的河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到我的壳上来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空怀疑地看了看老龟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么知道能不能相信你？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一路上妖怪都在等着我师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们都想吃了我的师父。”八戒补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证我不会伤害唐僧的。”老龟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想帮助他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧一行人犹豫了一会儿，走上了老龟的壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老龟开始向河对岸游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民们从树桩后面走了出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向唐僧他们挥手告别。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见！”一个女人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们回大唐的时候，一定要来看我们！”另一个人大声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会的，我保证！”唐僧大声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，老龟就离河岸很远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老龟回头看了看唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，你可以帮我一个忙吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”唐僧说，“你需要我做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经在这里修行上千年了。”老龟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我现在还是只老龟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你能帮我问一下佛祖，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我什么时候才能修成人身吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧点点头。“我会问他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时后，老龟游到了河的对岸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧他们上了岸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”老龟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请不要忘了帮我问佛祖我的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老龟潜入水下消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧上了马。一行人继续赶路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和往常一样，八戒很快就开始抱怨了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我走不动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望我们可以骑着那老龟去西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别抱怨了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里的路很平坦，已经很好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又走了几个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来他们要走山路，越往上，路越难走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒抱怨起来。“这路太难走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵寒风吹过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”悟净哆嗦起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”唐僧指着前方说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不远处的山上有个很大的庙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我们可以在那里休息一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看那座庙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的顶上笼罩着一层黑雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个地方不太好，我们不去那里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得挺好啊。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以看到凡人看不见的东西。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到那庙上有一层黑雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面可能有妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，传来了一阵咕噜咕噜声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看四周，想知道那声音是从哪里来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒拍了拍肚子。“抱歉，我有点儿饿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都又累又饿。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们就去那座庙吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行。”悟空厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呆在这里。我去找食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看唐僧，又警告了他一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对不能去那座庙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>